subject: College Athletics
Football
lead_paragraph: Florida State’s E. J. Manuel stopped a South Carolina rally and lead Florida State to a 26-17 victory over the turnover-plagued Gamecocks on Friday night in the Chick-fil-A Bowl in Atlanta.
